### 5. Implement policy priority ordering
- **File**: [engine.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/policy/engine.py#L31-L37)
- **Implementation**: Rules are sorted by [priority](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/tests/test_policy.py#186-207) (ascending) and then `action` ("deny" before "allow") in [load_rules](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/policy/engine.py#24-44).
```python
        self.rules = sorted(
            raw_rules,
            key=lambda x: (
                x.get("priority", 999),
                0 if x.get("action") == "deny" else 1,
            ),
        )
```

