- **Implementation**: [_enforce_retention](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/store.py#149-172) evicts or archives old segments when `max_events` is exceeded.

### 17. Implement unsubscribe() on EventBus
- **File**: [bus.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/bus.py#L251-L256)
